overview: Renaissance's Turn of the Cards and Scheherazade and Other Stories recorded live on  September 23, 2011 before a wildly enthusiastic sellout audience at Keswick Theater, Glenside, Philadelphia.  Acoustic Guitar, Vocals - Michael Dunford, Bass Guitar, Vocals – David J. Keyes  Drums, Percussion, Vocals – Frank Pagano, Keyboards – Rave Tesar, Keyboards, Vocals – Jason Hart  Lead Vocals – Annie Haslam
title: Renaissance: Live In Concert Tour 2011
